title: Key Characteristics of AI Agents
items: AI agents are autonomous systems designed to gather data, make decisions, and execute tasks.
They utilize advanced algorithms and machine learning techniques to process large amounts of data and make informed decisions.
AI agents possess proactive behavior, allowing them to initiate actions rather than merely responding to external prompts.
They exhibit goal-oriented behavior, setting specific objectives and mapping out steps to achieve them.
